        &nbsp; My research addresses computer networks architectures and <br>
        &nbsp; protocols - with focus on wireless access technologies <br>
        &nbsp; (including wireless sensor and actuation networks).<br>
        <br>
        &nbsp; I have been alerted by the vision of growing expenses <br>
